OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778771468
OL,3,C'We will come for you': Thousands of
OL,4,Ccounterfeit cigarettes seized
OL,6,FTrading Standards have said "we will
OL,7,Fcome for you" in a message to those
OL,8,Fselling counterfeit cigarettes and
OL,9,Ftobacco after thousands were seized
OL,10,Facross Oxfordshire as part of a recent
OL,11,Fcrackdown.
OL,13,FIn total, 5,900 counterfeit and
OL,14,Fsmuggled cigarettes and 950 grams of
OL,15,Fhand rolling tobacco were confiscated
OL,16,Fduring the most recent operation on 1
OL,17,FMay 2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
