OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778771468
OL,3,C'We will come for you': Thousands of
OL,4,Ccounterfeit cigarettes seized
OL,6,FThis followed raids in March, when
OL,7,Fofficers found more than 13,000
OL,8,Fillicit cigarettes, almost nine
OL,9,Fkilograms of illegal tobacco products,
OL,10,Fnicotine pouches and single use vapes
OL,11,Fat seven locations across Cowley and
OL,12,FHeadington.
OL,14,FThe efforts form part of Operation
OL,15,FCeCe, a national initiative funded by
OL,16,FHMRC and led by National Trading
OL,17,FStandards to tackle the illegal
OL,18,Ftobacco trade.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
