PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778771468
OL,3,C'We will come for you': Thousands of
OL,4,Ccounterfeit cigarettes seized
OL,6,FDavina Walkin, Operations Manager at
OL,7,FTrading Standards said: "We are
OL,8,Frelentless at Oxfordshire County
OL,9,FCouncil Trading Standards.
OL,11,F"In terms of protecting our youngsters
OL,12,F, often these products are really
OL,13,Fcheap and so they're appealing to the
OL,14,Fyoungsters.
OL,16,F"In terms of serious and organised
OL,17,Fcrime, we don't want it in the county
OL,18,Fand we're just there to protect our
OL,19,Fconsumers, so therefore I would say
OL,20,Fdon't sell these products because we
OL,21,Fwill come for you."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
