FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778771468
OL,3,C'We will come for you': Thousands of
OL,4,Ccounterfeit cigarettes seized
OL,6,FMs Walkin continued: "These cigarettes
OL,7,Fare made in unhealthy environments.
OL,8,FOften they're not monitored in any
OL,9,Fway. And so you really don't know what
OL,10,Fyou're smoking."
OL,12,FCouncillor Jenny Hannaby, Oxfordshire
OL,13,FCounty Council's Cabinet Member for
OL,14,FCommunity Safety, added: "We hear
OL,15,Fpeople's concerns about the changing
OL,16,Fface of their high streets and the
OL,17,Frise of shops used as fronts for
OL,18,Fcrime. Our message is simple: stop
OL,19,Ffunding organised crime.
